<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Poha Recipe</title>
	<link href="~/css/poha.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

    

    <div class="recipe-container">
        <h1>🥣 Poha</h1>
        

        <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
        <ul class="ingredients-list">
            <li>1 cup Poha (Flattened Rice)</li>
            <li>1 tbsp Oil</li>
            <li>1 tsp Mustard Seeds</li>
            <li>1 Green Chili (Chopped)</li>
            <li>1 Small Onion (Chopped)</li>
            <li>1 Small Potato (Chopped)</li>
            <li>1/4 cup Peanuts</li>
            <li>1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder</li>
            <li>Salt to taste</li>
            <li>1 tsp Sugar (Optional)</li>
            <li>1 tbsp Lemon Juice</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Coriander Leaves (Chopped)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <h3>Step 1: Prepare the Poha</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Rinse the poha in water for 30 seconds and drain. Let it sit for 5 minutes.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 2: Prepare the Tempering</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Heat oil in a pan and add mustard seeds.</li>
            <li>Once they splutter, add green chilies and peanuts. Sauté until golden.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 3: Cook the Vegetables</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Add chopped onions and potatoes. Cook until potatoes are soft.</li>
            <li>Add turmeric and salt, mix well.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 4: Add Poha</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Add the soaked poha and mix gently.</li>
            <li>Cook for 2 minutes, then add sugar (if using) and lemon juice.</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Step 5: Garnish & Serve</h3>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Garnish with fresh coriander leaves.</li>
            <li>Serve hot with tea or chutney.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
